      "id": "dd100000-0006-4000-8000-000000000006",
      "name": "OneSignal create notification",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1300, 220]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Daily digest — OneSignal\n\n**Schedule:** cron `0 10 * * *` (10:00 every day, timezone = n8n instance).\n\n**Workflow config:** fill `supabase_url`, `supabase_service_role_key`, `onesignal_app_id`, `onesignal_rest_api_key`, optional `lookback_hours` (default 24), `new_item_radius_km` (0 = all users minus owner per item).\n\n**Supabase:** run SQL migrations: `add_push_notification_rpcs.sql` then `add_daily_digest_push_rpcs.sql`.\n\n**App:** OneSignal SDK must set **External User ID** = Supabase `user.id` for each logged-in user.\n\n**Limits:** OneSignal caps batch size for `include_external_user_ids`; split in Code if you exceed their limit.",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 440
      },
